<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">The /pause is required because you can not switch out your bandolier while you are casting.  Or you would not get the benifit of the focus.
<br />

<br />
I have found /pause 4 is just about the correct time to switch right after tash lands.  You might wanna try /pause 5 if you tend to have high lag.
<br />

<br />
/Bandolier Activate Tashicide 
<br />
/cast 6
<br />
/rsay TASH -- %T 
<br />
/pause 4 
<br />
/Bandolier Activate Standard 
<br />

<br />
Psychoactive</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
